Telangana
Dec 11, 2014
Rape
Description:
			A deaf and dumb girl was allegedly gang-raped by four people yesterday night at Ayinavolu village of Wardhannapet mandal.

According to the girl's parents, the girl had gone out to answer nature's call at about 11 pm, when four drunk youth tied up her hands and allegedly gang-raped her.

After the girl's father found her, he called his son and villagers.

In the morning, they went to the Wardhannapet police station and lodged a complaint.

The police sent her for medical examination to CKM Maternity Hospital, Warangal.

Four suspects have been taken into police custody and the case is being investigated.


